{"tid":546542,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【23:07】衛報：英國沒有簽署「一帶一路」備忘錄","createTime":"2018-01-31T15:25:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-02T12:01:52.000Z","uid":147314,"like":108,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":54,"replies":[{"pid":"74b2cd5a4f4c0d30b950be6f038df8db3de22c00","tid":546542,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T15:25:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.theguardian.com/politics/2018/jan/31/theresa-may-holds-off-backing-china-900bn-pound-silk-road-strategy\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fpolitics%2F2018%2Fjan%2F31%2Ftheresa-may-holds-off-backing-china-900bn-pound-silk-road-strategy&d=J%2BGjt9OVN8jpNQuOpJCvz49%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=b76c05ce\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.theguardian.com/politics/2018/jan/31/theresa-may-holds-off-backing-china-900bn-pound-silk-road-strategy</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Government sources confirmed the UK did not sign a memorandum of understanding giving Britain&rsquo;s official endorsement to the $900bn Belt and Road Initiative, which is President Xi Jinping&rsquo;s personal project.</span> Critics say it is designed to pull other countries in the region deeper into China&rsquo;s sphere of influence and could give unfair preferential treatment to Chinese contractors."},{"pid":"ecde1da30d6cc94df3e8e5233d773acc8f4db195","tid":546542,"uid":147314,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T15:26:34.000Z","msg":"Theresa May holds off backing China's &pound;900bn Silk Road strategy<br />\n<br />\nPM says UK is &lsquo;natural partner&rsquo; but fails to sign off on Xi Jinping&rsquo;s personal project<br />\n<br />\nJessica Elgot in Beijing<br />\nWed 31 Jan 2018 15.07 GMT<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.guim.co.uk/img/media/5432baa3be35cf8d4055ac4745317309eab688b1/955_303_3545_2126/master/3545.jpg?w=620&amp;q=55&amp;auto=format&amp;usm=12&amp;fit=max&amp;s=f54aff10a9e9e89c51a57268b97ce0c3\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.guim.co.uk%2Fimg%2Fmedia%2F5432baa3be35cf8d4055ac4745317309eab688b1%2F955_303_3545_2126%2Fmaster%2F3545.jpg%3Fw%3D620%26q%3D55%26auto%3Dformat%26usm%3D12%26fit%3Dmax%26s%3Df54aff10a9e9e89c51a57268b97ce0c3&h=c03c4274&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nTheresa May has sidestepped a Chinese push for a formal endorsement of its $900bn Silk Road strategy, suggesting Britain still has concerns about China&rsquo;s political objectives for the huge infrastructure project."},{"pid":"55446abb81a8ee2bb122e7a50259be32fea3f678","tid":546542,"uid":10890,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T15:27:12.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;Unfair preferential treatment to Chinese contractors&rdquo;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19113043830d0fd2c00364a155fa2a6279f55841","tid":546542,"uid":147314,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T15:27:30.000Z","msg":"Government sources confirmed the UK did not sign a memorandum of understanding giving Britain&rsquo;s official endorsement to the $900bn Belt and Road Initiative, which is President Xi Jinping&rsquo;s personal project. Critics say it is designed to pull other countries in the region deeper into China&rsquo;s sphere of influence and could give unfair preferential treatment to Chinese contractors.<br />\n<br />\nIn a press conference in Beijing on Wednesday with the Chinese premier, Li Keqiang, May said the UK was &ldquo;a natural partner&rdquo; for the project but stopped short of giving the scheme her unequivocal backing.<br />\n<br />\nInstead, May, who is on her first bilateral trip to China, said the two countries would continue to work together &ldquo;to identify how best we can co-operate on Belt and Road across the region and ensure it meets international standards&rdquo;, indicating that agreement may not yet have been reached."},{"pid":"0eb95932cdacb25d38ef431cb634f3a67a6efa8a","tid":546542,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T15:28:33.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;There wasn&rsquo;t a memorandum signed,&rdquo; a UK government official said. &ldquo;They both spoke positively about the potential impacts it could have, but it&rsquo;s important it&rsquo;s implemented in the right way. They are going to carry on talking.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\nBeijing had hoped to seal the UK&rsquo;s backing after the chancellor, Philip Hammond, attended the Belt and Road Forum for International Cooperation in Beijing last year. China still lacks a major western endorsement, with Australia, France, Germany, the European commission and the US yet to give it their unqualified backing.<br />\n<br />\nOn a visit to China earlier this year, the French president, Emmanuel Macron, said he had reservations and that the initiative should benefit the region, not be a &ldquo;one way street&rdquo;."},{"pid":"a37bd6c12f94bd95af41cfa6e7487feb8c018ed4","tid":546542,"uid":147314,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T15:30:53.000Z","msg":"太長唔copy哂"},{"pid":"b5e5aedbdd949f719c121f48b2262f4bf2f21c94","tid":546542,"uid":4783,"like":56,"dislike":1,"score":55,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T15:33:06.000Z","msg":"簡單講，英國因為話一帶一路既項目達唔到國際標準既公開透明，所以唔會簽，以免上身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而中方就好想逼may姐簽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d55ce7ce630118c0a833c38c096ae31b71e53882","tid":546542,"uid":76310,"like":61,"dislike":0,"score":61,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T15:33:08.000Z","msg":"(賺埋5毛的錢)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一帶一路咁成功, 咁有策略, 咁有遠見, 唔加入只會係呢個沒落國家的損失"},{"pid":"0c918ac4a6a450ba3721808ab88326cb0df1dfdc","tid":546542,"uid":138441,"like":3,"dislike":7,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T15:38:16.000Z","msg":"英國佬奶中國奶到雪雪聲<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47f2987aaec467d5eca44223abf28349dd141953","tid":546542,"uid":34103,"like":2,"dislike":76,"score":-74,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T15:39:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"24876ee72982bca8d4ca77125b463e313fc9c1b0","tid":546542,"uid":61280,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T15:39:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>(賺埋5毛的錢)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一帶一路咁成功, 咁有策略, 咁有遠見, 唔加入只會係呢個沒落國家的損失</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00ae7725b0d612396efaeaaf1149216364ce7603","tid":546542,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0c918ac4a6a450ba3721808ab88326cb0df1dfdc","tid":546542,"uid":138441,"like":3,"dislike":7,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T15:38:16.000Z","msg":"英國佬奶中國奶到雪雪聲<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T15:40:10.000Z","msg":"英國佬最現實"},{"pid":"1067d38e695d1ce6140fb52cc50c340a6d79f3d9","tid":546542,"uid":147314,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T15:44:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.ft.com/content/3e79ae14-0681-11e8-9650-9c0ad2d7c5b5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.com%2Fcontent%2F3e79ae14-0681-11e8-9650-9c0ad2d7c5b5&d=J%2BGjt9OVN8jpNQuOpJCvz49%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=e2a54be3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ft.com/content/3e79ae14-0681-11e8-9650-9c0ad2d7c5b5</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">May resists pressure to endorse China&rsquo;s &lsquo;new silk road&rsquo; project<br />\n<br />\nUK and France among nations declining to sign MOU supporting Belt and Road Initiative</span>"},{"pid":"dbb456a4c1ae45ae7d2acfe7acf7da6bc0a61f4a","tid":546542,"uid":147314,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T15:45:34.000Z","msg":"Theresa May has refused to give written support for China&rsquo;s &ldquo;new silk road&rdquo; project amid concerns in the west that contracts for the huge infrastructure scheme are not transparent and favour Chinese companies.<br />\n<br />\nAfter weeks of tensions over the Belt and Road Initiative, the UK prime minister refused to sign a proposed memorandum of understanding, viewed by Beijing as an important signal of western support for President Xi Jinping&rsquo;s signature project.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;There wasn&rsquo;t a memorandum of understanding signed,&rdquo; Mrs May&rsquo;s aides confirmed. One person close to the negotiations said <span style=\"color: red;\">China had been pressing the prime minister to sign a declaration &ldquo;since before Christmas&rdquo;.</span>"},{"pid":"58807c0f8bd8d80d66c9040af4fa913ea19a76b7","tid":546542,"uid":60545,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T15:46:23.000Z","msg":"支那狗同五毛冇得打J<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb77ca1480ad463e9dd3cfc771b2196a11d645cc","tid":546542,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T15:49:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote> ... President Xi Jinping&rsquo;s personal project.</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bf258e71a44e18083a4d2589d991378680c96f5","tid":546542,"uid":4783,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"dbb456a4c1ae45ae7d2acfe7acf7da6bc0a61f4a","tid":546542,"uid":147314,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T15:45:3